contentrichtext.text: {{Unreferenced|date=December 2009}} <table border=1 cellpadding=2 cellspacing=0 align=right style=margin-left:1em> <caption><span style="font-size:140%;">'''Kettil Karlsson (Vasa)'''</span></caption> <tr valign=top><td>'''Regency'''<td>February, 1464 <br> - interregnum - <br> - August 11, 1465 <tr valign=top><td>'''Family'''<td>[[House of Vasa|Vasa]] <tr valign=top><td>'''Predecessor'''<td>[[Christian I of Sweden]] <tr valign=top><td>'''Interregnum'''<td>[[Charles VIII of Sweden]] <tr valign=top><td>'''Successor'''<td>[[Jöns Bengtsson Oxenstierna|Jöns Bengtsson (Oxenstierna)]] <tr valign=top><td>'''Date of Birth'''<td>1433 <tr valign=top><td>'''Date of Death'''<td>August 11, 1465 </table> '''Kettil Karlsson (Vasa)''' (1433 – August 11, 1465) was a [[Sweden|Swedish]] clergyman and regent of [[Sweden]] under the [[Kalmar Union]] from February 1464 to August 1465, interluded by a six-month interregnum of king [[Charles VIII of Sweden]]. He was also [[Bishop of Linköping]]. He was the son of Karl Kristiernsson ([[House of Vasa|Vasa]]) and Ebba Eriksdotter (Krummedige). {{S-start}} {{S-hou|[[House of Vasa]]||1433|August 11|1465|}} {{S-rel|ca}} {{S-bef|before=[[Nils König]]}} {{S-ttl|title=[[Bishop of Linköping]]|years=1459–1465}} {{S-aft|after=[[Henrik Tidemansson]]}} {{End}} {{Monarchs of Sweden}} {{Persondata |name= Kettil Karlsson |alternative names= |short description= Regent of Sweden |date of birth= 1433 |place of birth= |date of death=August 11, 1465 |place of death= }} {{DEFAULTSORT:Kettil Karlsson}} [[Category:Rulers of Finland]] [[Category:Regents of Sweden]] [[Category:Bishops of Linköping]] [[Category:1433 births]] [[Category:1465 deaths]] [[Category:15th-century Swedish people]] {{Sweden-bio-stub}} {{Bishop-stub}}
